{
  "stem": "22586.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why the name was called Uchorod, because it was named after the river.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also there was a, a castle just above the river and the name horod mean-- I think it's in Russian-- or in Czech-- meant castle.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So castle on the Uz, on the river Uz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where the name of the town came from.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Uchorod.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was a wine merchant, and mother, my mother was just homemaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had a maid who was-- who lived with us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, she had the house cleaning and laundry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was mainly it because my mother did all the cooking.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- the maid did the house cleaning and the laundry, ironing, that, that type of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Apartment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was on the street that the main market was on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The, the market-- we didn't have big supermarkets like we have here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, for instance, produce and chickens, geese, ducks, and all these things, you bought-- the poultry, you bought it live at the market.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people from surrounding towns-- farmers-- used to bring their produce and livestock into town every day, but especially on Thursdays, I think.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the market was set up right in our street, on Bozos Utca.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The produce, farmers were mainly Bulgarians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- so they-- they would bring in the produce and fruits and, and vegetables.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we would buy it-- go to the market and buy it all the time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was set up right in front of our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would be out there in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "By twelve or one o'clock in the afternoon, it was all cleaned up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You wouldn't know there was a market there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- but-- and also, the street we lived on was a continuation of Masaryk [?",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
